1. *Pucajte* u metu. (Shoot at the target.)
2. Morate da *pucajte* u pokretu. (You have to shoot on the move.)
3. Oni su počeli da *pucaju* na nas. (They started shooting at us.)
4. Nemojte *pucati* u vazduh. (Don't shoot in the air.)
5. Moram da *pucam* na ovaj cilj. (I have to shoot at this target.)
6. *Pucaj* kad god budeš spreman. (Shoot whenever you're ready.)
7. Ovo je poslednji put da *pucaš* u mene. (This is the last time you shoot at me.)
8. Oni su me videli da *pucaju* na cilj. (They saw me shooting at the target.)
9. Nisam mogao *da puca* iz pištolja. (I couldn't shoot from the gun.)
10. Kada *budeš pucao*, drži pištolj čvrsto. (When you shoot, hold the gun tightly.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "pucajte" is the imperative form of the verb "pucati" which means "to shoot".